      "content": "that makes sense but it's still super frustrating. so basically most of my money is just disappearing into interest instead of actually paying off what i owe? it almost feels like there are hidden things eating away at the payment before it even hits the principal. can you help me understand the math a bit more specifically? like if i have a certain amount of interest accruing daily or monthly, how does that interplay with the payment amount?",
